# LastMinute ITR — Architect rule

Before building or changing filing flows, read and follow:

- `docs/CURSOR_MASTER_PROMPT.md` (full Cursor master prompt)
- `docs/BLOG_PLATFORM_GAP_MATRIX.md` (blog → platform status)
- `frontend/lib/ai/aiMasterPromptContext.ts` (document section routing for AI)

Key invariants:

1. Engine (`backend/engine`) is L1 truth — AI never invents tax numbers.
2. Mark unfinished Payment / AI integrations with `PAYMENT_API_TODO` / `AI_API_TODO`.
3. Keep UI in simple English wizards (doc 40: Answer → Upload → Fix → Number → File).
4. AY 2026-27: multi Form 16 single std deduction, 87A ₹12L, VDA 30% no loss netting, F&O BP buckets, HRA least-of-three, 80D no cash.
